As was predicted in the columns of THE TIMES on Tuesday last, Mayor Wickham yesterday removed Police Commissioners Matsell and Disbecker and appointed in their places Messrs. Dewitt C. Wheeler and Joel B. Erhardt. Messrs. Matsell and Disbecker were officially notified of their removal at 6:30 P. M., and an hour later a meeting of the new board was held.
